---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Policies"
description: "Uncost's governance policies — public review drafts. Not adopted or in force; publication is not adoption."
---
{% from "partials/content-needed.njk" import block as gap %}
<section class="blk blk--first">
  <p class="eyebrow">Policies</p>
  <h1 class="sec">Governance, in the open.</h1>
  <p class="lead">Public review drafts. Not adopted or in force — publication is not adoption. Each is published so it can be reviewed before it is ever activated.</p>
</section>
<section class="blk blk--cream2">
  <div class="doc-list">
{%- for policy in catalog.policies %}
    <a class="doc-row" href="/policies/{{ policy.slug }}/"><span class="doc-id">{{ policy.id }}</span><span class="doc-title">{{ policy.display }}</span><span class="status status--planned">Draft</span></a>
{%- endfor %}
  </div>
  <p class="doc-note">The consolidated policy pack is maintained in the public repository: <a href="https://github.com/uncost-org/uncost/blob/main/policies/POLICY-PACK-v1.3.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Policy Pack v1.3</a>.</p>
</section>
